title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea Season 4 E1-13 X264 AC3
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea
Season Four
Episodes 1 through 13

It's what you've been waiting for!

This set is from a combination of sources and surpasses the "official" release in quality.

- Each episode begins with the season four "In Color" special opening
- Audio quality has been enhanced

- Most episodes include previews for the next episode
